2ï¸âƒ£ Escrow Flow (heart of trust)

This is non-negotiable for BizSwap credibility.

Escrow lifecycle

1. Buyer initiates transaction


2. Funds go into escrow (not seller)


3. Listing locks


4. Seller delivers ownership/partnership terms


5. Buyer confirms OR dispute timer expires


6. Funds released OR refunded



Core rule

> BizSwap never assumes trust. Escrow enforces it.



Release conditions examples:

Manual buyer approval

Auto-release after X days

Admin arbitration (dispute)



